	* build.wsf: Rename stdlib to stdcxx.
	* generate.wsf: Ditto.
	* makelog.wsf: Ditto.
	* projects.js: Ditto. Rename out library name from
	stdlib.[lib|dll] to libstd.[lib|dll] to consistency
	with unix names
	* runall.wsf: The same.

