2006-08-20  Martin Sebor  <sebor@roguewave.com>

	* collate.cpp ("podarray.cc"): Removed #include directive
	to prevent multiple definition errors.
	(__rw_pod_array): Moved explicit instantiation...
	* podarray.h: ...to here.

