	variable to -1 for icc-9.1 - buildlog.htm is unicode.
	* msvc-config.js (solutionICC91): New variable to keep icc-9.1 
	solution object.
	* runall.wsf (runAllExamples): Set logUnicode variable to "true"
	for icc-9.1 - buildlog.htm is unicode.

