	STDCXX-71
	* cerrno: Avoided #undefining errno.
	* errno.h: Same.
	* _defs.h: Used quotes instead of pointy brackets in the defintion
	of the _RWSTD_ANSI_C_ERRNO_H and _RWSTD_CERRNO macros to prevent
	the errno macro from expanding.

